QuestData.Title: Down in the Deeps
QuestData.Description: <Jinky rolls up her sleeves and slicks back her hair while eyeing you up and down.>$B$BFine, if Fizzle wants you to have your own boat, the first thing we'll need is parts. Guess who gets to go get them?$B$B<Jinky smiles as she points downward and then grabs you a spare diving helm and flippers.>$B$BThat's right, $g brother : sister;. You get to go down into the deeps and salvage what rocket car parts you can find at the Raceway Ruins.
QuestData.CompletionText: I'm not punching the timecard on this one until you get me everything that's on that parts list.
